text: Willy Klein (11 October 1912 - 15 July 2004) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Dudelange
